{"tid":1418073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"乖啦，勇武手足俾我哋接下你哋更好無？","createTime":"2019-08-05T17:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T19:10:02.000Z","uid":135000,"like":58,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3e7e638be029ba8171ce96b9856b96a391e0e418","tid":1418073,"uid":135000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:47:04.000Z","msg":"對唔住頭先做咗標題黨，重新開返一個先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一次出post，絕非割蓆，但一向都係和理非嘅我經過今日都俾少少意見。<br />\n少長，想fast read嘅自己睇紅字，求下大家睇埋先屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勇武手足，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我求你哋嚟緊休息下回下氣</span></span>。今日燒狗屋掟波仔，我雖然心裡好認同，但難免一定會有淺黃嘅人覺得過咗火。係，你可能會覺得要歸邊一早歸咗，但無可否認嘅係仲有好多中間嘅牆頭草，見到白衫打人會變黃，見到黑衫反抗會變藍。我明白大家見到啲狗越嚟越過份會好嬲，我都好嬲，我睇直播都會喊，但呢幾日就交俾我哋班和理非同文宣都捉住嚟打，乖啦我哋換下更好無？<span style=\"color: red;\">啲狗俾人撚係有人工收㗎，但我哋俾人拉多一個就弱一分㗎啦</span>，你到時就連原本想上嗰啲都縮埋，<span style=\"color: red;\">咁就一切都完㗎啦</span>。<br />\n<br />\n有巴打會覺得叫勇武停，就會俾對家有時間去拉人開始清算。依家唔係叫佢哋完全停，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只係休息</span></span>。就算依家日日勇武，日日be water，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">都依然有幾十個手足俾人拉</span></span>。我哋係要勇武，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但唔係要勇武住去送頭，送對手去俾人扣</span></span>。<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">乖啦，換更，take turns，落場唞下好無？</span></span>仲記唔記得朴槿惠係點下台？？唔係單靠勇武日日出去打江山，和理非嘅堅持都好重要！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非派，今日罷工都勉強叫成功，但好多人係一日罷工佢可以，但連續罷就會<span style=\"color: red;\">攞咗佢條命</span>。以上兩班人嘅民意都好重要，納粹黨就係因為爭取到民意會一舉成為最大黨；中共就係因為爭取到班農民嘅民意所以先贏到國民黨。當然仲有好多其他因素，但民意的確係其中一個勝利嘅原因。以前我都認為民意冇用，但去到呢個樽頸位，<span style=\"color: red;\">我哋嘅籌碼剩返唔多</span>，對家已經出晒舊招打民意戰，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我哋就更加唔可以再重蹈覆轍輸同樣嘅嘢。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">機場集會絕對可以成為嚟緊嘅大方向</span></span>，而且必須係和理非回合。726同啱啱都有去機場，相信大家都會發現：<br />\n1. 雖然係今晚少咗遊客同埋我哋人唔多，但眼見我哋氣勢好好，好多遊客都支持我哋。<br />\n2. 收哂啲搵食撚皮，佢有佢哋返工，我有我哋宣傳。<br />\n3. 位置同地區雖然險要，但最危險即係最安全嘅地方，班狗係唔會敢郁手。只要<span style=\"color: red;\">幾次集會無狗嘅情況下都和平散去</span>，我哋就可以更顯得出啲狗嘅劣根性。尤其係依家日日有記者會嘅情況下，運用得好更加可以拎嚟反擊。<br />\n<br />\n同一時間地區文宣同民間記者會都要keep住做，絕對唔可以有一刻鬆懈。<br />\n冷氣軍師同和理非係時候要全面出動接勇武手足更。荃灣單嘢，<span style=\"color: red;\">依家開始吃盡奶力去煲大佢！將焦點放返係警黑合作度！！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定個時間表，係時候嚟返次百萬人大遊行。<br />\n（雖然唔知批唔批，要買重保險咪籌棋囉屌）<br />\n<br />\n雖說老土，但：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">欲速則不達，擒賊先擒王。</span></span><br />\n一子錯，滿盤皆落索。<br />\n記唔記得我哋嘅初衷係乜嘢？？<br />\n係五大訴求，缺一不可！！<br />\n我哋做緊嘅只係手段，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好俾憤怒同仇恨將佢變成目的</span>！<br />\n唔好將自己變成自己討厭嘅人！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">對準政權，切勿分化！</span></span>"},{"pid":"edde7c2d8af4459af615f15e1ab46ab15ba5fbd4","tid":1418073,"uid":135000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:48:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b671b9dbbe095a6b2684a902ce77410cc66f772","tid":1418073,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:49:20.000Z","msg":"求求大家，盡快去換美元現鈔！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1417102\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1417102</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e3731090635a2a2127a4b1c0f95748ded227fbf5","tid":1418073,"uid":135000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:49:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e491d86a1cb5a1fdbe1a8f61db775f0c5f61339","tid":1418073,"uid":68471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:49:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a4fcaad88dca45bfc019c837109edf38675a7147","tid":1418073,"uid":131842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:49:34.000Z","msg":"全港流浪狗位置實時地圖上線啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1406448/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1406448/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/cAzgTon.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcAzgTon.png&h=5d46c5a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n是咁的，本人寫左個好似google doc咁既地圖<br />\n<br />\n睇緊live既即刻入黎幫手報料!<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkmap.live/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmap.live%2F&d=bDHmYwogulq9FkNLxWxOtmXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=db9faaf6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkmap.live/</a><br />\n見到多狗, 即刻mark番落地圖<br />\n視乎數量就算已經報左都可以報多一次<br />\n幫手傳出去 等義士唔好再食布袋戰術<br />\nBe Water!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1406448/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1406448/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hkmap.live/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmap.live%2F&d=bDHmYwogulq9FkNLxWxOtmXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=db9faaf6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkmap.live/</a>"},{"pid":"1352ce1a982f4273e607fadadf1356cb00f1dbf1","tid":1418073,"uid":135000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:49:58.000Z","msg":"屌我都好，求下大家睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99de7a781714cd32b6764615e0ef9ca4ebd0c3f8","tid":1418073,"uid":135000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:50:18.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"8ef30004e6e70cbeabef6c634a6a48fcd7cb2ee9","tid":1418073,"uid":27085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:50:33.000Z","msg":"[人手置頂][有圖]反思到底下一步點先係可行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1417708\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1417708</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7620b0bfa6ef78fdddab0886342c9ee26a97ba8c","tid":1418073,"uid":135000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:51:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45989885229b9f06358aeff15022a7db72684508","tid":1418073,"uid":296677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:51:42.000Z","msg":"同感 <br />\n<br />\n利申：放核彈都唔割蓆"},{"pid":"40a5e7437939d37c6dd3f7aa9a59348f32ea4d94","tid":1418073,"uid":135000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45989885229b9f06358aeff15022a7db72684508","tid":1418073,"uid":296677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:51:42.000Z","msg":"同感 <br />\n<br />\n利申：放核彈都唔割蓆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:53:03.000Z","msg":"利申：絕對支持前線打撚柒班黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢哋放核彈都會保護佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5fb3f75fe366210be71dc67984793dd7dcf669","tid":1418073,"uid":135000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:53:40.000Z","msg":"推！！"},{"pid":"928883c002ab721e3bdb27c8b495ae8a59e3733f","tid":1418073,"uid":258098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:53:43.000Z","msg":"我唔知你哋連仔和理非咩事<br />\n但係係FACEBOOK 裡面嘅和理非爸爸媽媽<br />\n到宜家都冇割席 反而連仔日日有人屌我哋"},{"pid":"3268ead60b8b6453f1bdd272ddbe62a7238edc22","tid":1418073,"uid":101623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:54:49.000Z","msg":"唔好令自己變到同廢老藍絲冇分別！  正如大師兄講，唔好俾仇恨支配自己。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1417694\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1417694</a>"},{"pid":"0604c157f2b3caf3b0eff736026a18c6a6e71b19","tid":1418073,"uid":135000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"928883c002ab721e3bdb27c8b495ae8a59e3733f","tid":1418073,"uid":258098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:53:43.000Z","msg":"我唔知你哋連仔和理非咩事<br />\n但係係FACEBOOK 裡面嘅和理非爸爸媽媽<br />\n到宜家都冇割席 反而連仔日日有人屌我哋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:55:56.000Z","msg":"無屌前線呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見着日日俾人拉幾十個好肉赤咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc4fa8fd1b546f4bf10b9c22c932738433f3ee5","tid":1418073,"uid":23373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:56:05.000Z","msg":"夜左就無人覆,幫你推推啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431d3e5987aed289951d26e8bbb53d008469dbcf","tid":1418073,"uid":135000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cc4fa8fd1b546f4bf10b9c22c932738433f3ee5","tid":1418073,"uid":23373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:56:05.000Z","msg":"夜左就無人覆,幫你推推啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:57:02.000Z","msg":"大家仲有好多嘢要關注，我都明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e6dbace9e9ba96020d833e4470b16a3f202ad5","tid":1418073,"uid":272840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:57:37.000Z","msg":"求下大家俾我d文宣上場啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"546cbfb259466a634a0a22ebf062d2cad91e4392","tid":1418073,"uid":135000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8e6dbace9e9ba96020d833e4470b16a3f202ad5","tid":1418073,"uid":272840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:57:37.000Z","msg":"求下大家俾我d文宣上場啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:00:24.000Z","msg":"Airdrop連儂牆戰士隨時ready!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0886ee44bb2bb56e602a399437acde40e22b54e9","tid":1418073,"uid":129348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:01:19.000Z","msg":"的確真係應該輪到和理非回合"},{"pid":"869135909d86aa3638cd0f75c8a584633c089cbd","tid":1418073,"uid":135000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0886ee44bb2bb56e602a399437acde40e22b54e9","tid":1418073,"uid":129348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:01:19.000Z","msg":"的確真係應該輪到和理非回合"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:03:14.000Z","msg":"我真心好想佢哋唞下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我企住曬太陽都覺得好攰，<br />\n我想像唔到佢哋上前線先要打一日有幾撚崩潰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79f529faa1302152426770242de2d9a97c3a6b4e","tid":1418073,"uid":135000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:03:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"401e163ba6604f30d8d8974fd3192a7c83dd820d","tid":1418073,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:04:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4724b3d89a93ae4d438cc80a777789ad6685d6e8","tid":1418073,"uid":230152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:05:35.000Z","msg":"push"}]}